<h4 id="2002">2002</h4>
<p>Braak, C.J., J.F. de Haan, J.W. Hovenier, and <span class="gissauthor">L.D. Travis</span>, 2002: <a href="https://pubs.giss.nasa.gov/abs/br06000k.html">Galileo photopolarimetry of Jupiter at 678.5 nm</a>. <cite>Icarus</cite>, <b>157</b>, 401-418, doi:10.1006/icar.2002.6846.</p>
